RdJL3SOaqMJsvjAplOTa3J8rEQ9jihcuoirNAS2U4vB1A_34clkNY7XmVz1F-LCH-QA7Vd1KesFormJhQCPCdtdr1ihQz208DPNY_XGNJ3950RoqX2moDaqBES-fKN2bQeacGHENmiinsJ38lGMb6HYa6g</a><br />\n<br />\n【求真】年初3名海關執勤時意外身亡，傳真社記者初時亦以為只是一般走私犯罪活動，未有進一步調查。直至收到報料，再留意到執法部門反走私行動的報告，才了解該處水域的走私活動絕非一般小規模犯罪，故決定展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社報道發表5日後，水警展開反走私行動，在沙洲以南水域截獲一艘快艇，艇上載有62箱、市值約4.5萬港元的懷疑走私凍肉。報道發表後14日，深圳公安在包括涉及凍肉走私的內伶仃水域執法，銷毀45艘走私船。<br />\n<br />\n我們日常接觸到一則新聞或消息，往往未必完全真確，或未能反映現實。這個年代流行fact check 事實查核，人人都會問這個「fact check咗未？」那個是否「fced? (fact-checked?) 」如不是親身前往三跑水域視察，亦不會驚嘆原來走私規模可以有近百艘船參與。在這個重視fced的年代，傳真社今個月正式成立 FactWire Fact Check 臉書專頁，幫你打假求真。<br />\n<br />\n加入月捐，撐起真相：<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus%2F&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=67fbf376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus/</a><br />\n報料：Whatsapp/Telegram 9639 7479"},{"pid":"aad621de383a037caa416f0848c75d3c826b5127","tid":1981011,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩開錯左台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead871e32f190751ff3d0254d6b32b51df14c894","tid":1981011,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4029b706cfd16328cfb4738943867f6b11316bff","tid":1981011,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T12:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a72f7bb919da5ee3fa2a64f6b7d2f8d6f5ba02","tid":1981011,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4029b706cfd16328cfb4738943867f6b11316bff","tid":1981011,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1